/T (Description Stores vehicle plate number, owner name, and type in the system. Calculates toll amount automatically based on vehicle type. Saves all payment records to transactions.txt with timestamps. Creates a dedicated receipt text file for each toll payment. Displays total revenue and vehicle count per toll booth. Allows full user interaction through a numbered console menu.)
/E (Description Stores vehicle plate number, owner name, and type in the system. Calculates toll amount automatically based on vehicle type. Saves all payment records to transactions.txt with timestamps. Creates a dedicated receipt text file for each toll payment. Displays total revenue and vehicle count per toll booth. Allows full user interaction through a numbered console menu.)
